{"tid":1976598,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"10人涉非法集結 被告投訴遭警打斷骨","createTime":"2020-04-17T10:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T12:33:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7393b2cddc222b2b3c0532d0a61c32bc824655","tid":1976598,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/7BQ3Z7OYX55W55J6BZCR4JJ47Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2F7BQ3Z7OYX55W55J6BZCR4JJ47Y%2F&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU935V8GO7j56WmnfPW9WRM38%3D&h=53e0dc31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2F7BQ3Z7OYX55W55J6BZCR4JJ47Y%2F&h=a559ada1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200417/7BQ3Z7OYX55W55J6BZCR4JJ47Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n10人涉非法集結<br />\n被告投訴遭警打斷骨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200417/large/1587055191_d1a3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200417%2Flarge%2F1587055191_d1a3.gif&h=c919f81c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年8月25日網民發起荃葵青遊行，及後有人在深水埗警署外聚集，警方驅散多人被捕。事隔近半年，10人昨日被落案控以非法集結。多名被告在庭上投訴，被捕時及在警車上遭到警暴，有被告被打至入院需縫上八針，有被告甚至骨折。另外，被控在旺角涉藏士巴拿摺刀的被告，亦投訴被警員威脅將汽油彈放入其背包。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：手足親筆信：勿因疫情忘公義<br />\n<br />\n另案警疑威脅硬塞汽油彈<br />\n<br />\n10名被告依次為葉姓男學生（17歲）、無業林嘉豐（36歲）、測量員林浩廷（28歲）、地盤工人林易津（25歲）、女被告韓紫彤（23歲）、侍應吳南海（20歲）、學生黃澤鋒（21歲）、學生唐恒輝（23歲）、港鐵技工龔漢文（23歲）及學生盧宇柏（19歲），涉於去年8月25日與蔡子聰在深水埗警署附近參與非法集結。首被告另被控在欽州街參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n辯方透露，首被告多次遭警員按在地上徒手及以警棍毆打、第三被告亦被打至左手前臂骨折、第四被告被捕時遭警員用警棍毆至流血，曾要求入院卻不獲理會，律師到場後始獲送院，小腿需縫上八針。<br />\n<br />\n於非法集結控罪中提及的男生蔡子聰（20歲），早前因涉及在深水埗持有雷射筆、而被控管有攻擊性武器罪，昨日被加控於荃灣參與暴動，控方要求將蔡的案件與上述10人案件合併處理。<br />\n<br />\n惟裁判官嚴舜儀質疑事發地點不同，兩案有何關聯，「唔通要十個人企晒喺法庭聽佢荃灣啲證供？」最終拒接納合併申請。兩案均於6月5日再訊以待轉介區域法院。<br />\n<br />\n另外，27歲張子軒被控11月1日凌晨在旺角藏士巴拿及摺刀，被控管有攻擊性武器罪，辯方昨投訴被告曾被警方傷及眼角，及有警員威脅將汽油彈置於其背包內。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC582、594、253/20"},{"pid":"d043b0867afd168e108f44c370e13e5323b6ebed","tid":1976598,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"推，毋忘手足"},{"pid":"abc6d65a58111a281b7b626762e649c2af9f76af","tid":1976598,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927beaeed8b397304bcbe41590a795674ff22a83","tid":1976598,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f071219f88722ad8e8e6682bc7ddc5f8d9be4d18","tid":1976598,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900488a8f660c25257d2b41406c3031111659397","tid":1976598,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"